## Dependency Direction (Enforced, CI Validated)

```text
types → config → lib → services → app
```

- Allowed: `services` imports `lib`, `app` imports `services`
- Forbidden: `lib` imports `services`, `services` imports `app`
- Forbidden: cross-layer direct access to internal implementations

Full guardrails: `docs/ai/03-guardrails.md`

---

## Forbidden Operations

- blocking: `console.log`, `: any`, `@ts-ignore`, `sk-...`, `Bearer ...`, `ghp_...`, `eval(`, `.innerHTML =`, `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`, hardcoded `http://` (non-localhost) are forbidden
- warning: `TODO:`, `FIXME:` will be flagged during validation; clean them up
- Direct reads of `process.env.*` are forbidden; use `config/env.ts` instead
- Direct SQL concatenation and storing tokens in localStorage are forbidden
- `git add .` is forbidden; developing features on `main` is forbidden
- Committing secrets, API keys, or passwords is forbidden

Full list: `docs/ai/03-guardrails.md`

